{"tid":708521,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(PC) Conan Exiles 開荒好累","createTime":"2018-06-19T11:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T03:35:53.000Z","uid":63669,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bebe46ef4deff1ebf262589901cc8d7e6c41e3c8","tid":708521,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T11:06:12.000Z","msg":"問: Conan Exiles係乜??<br />\n<br />\n答: Conan Exiles 係奇幻荒蠻版既方舟集冒險,求生,戰爭於一身既sandbox game<br />\n<br />\n問: Conan Exiles 有乜特色<br />\n<br />\n答: 在廣闊的世界中探險：探索巨大的世界，穿越南方的炙熱沙漠，攀登北方的覆雪群山。發現古老的文明、廢墟和地下城。<br />\n<br />\n生存：控制身體冷暖，注意飢餓口渴，抵御嚴酷的沙暴，探索黑暗地下城時保護自己的心智不會腐化，與狂暴的怪獸戰鬥，在艱苦的環境中活下去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tvcmw4qe\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftvcmw4qe&h=1124bb03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n建造：收集資源來制作工具和武器，一磚一瓦地從小小的住宅一直建造到整座城市。建造牆壁，制作陷阱和升降梯，等等。靈活運用各種不同的家具、工作站和 NPC 守衛來彰顯你的創意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/w680hsjq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fw680hsjq&h=63d853b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n稱霸：向敵人發起戰爭，使用攻城武器和爆炸物粉碎他們的城牆，在暴力和殘酷的戰鬥中釋放你的狂野怒火。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ve8g3iwz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fve8g3iwz&h=63780360&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n組建僕役大軍：抓捕 NPC，將他們拖回你的基地，然後用痛苦之輪令他們屈服。訓練他們成為弓箭手、工匠、藝人等，為你的大本營服務。<br />\n<br />\n化身神明：在神明的祭壇上獻祭你的敵人，召喚並控制巨型神之化身。讓敵人和他們的建築粉碎在化身的腳下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/s2qcgfou\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fs2qcgfou&h=91a33ad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ub5xcn6j\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fub5xcn6j&h=47c845a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />C版既 Conan Exiles 有連登團嗎??<br />\n<br />\n答: 我地前幾日係#1364 pvp server 由零開始建立連登部落，依家慢慢開始上左軌道。如果有人想一齊努力既可以直接入server 搵 生命中的過客 OR HomerSimpson 加你入團 或者 入我地TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/BlsobBB38IoVIDrct5mFQA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FBlsobBB38IoVIDrct5mFQA&d=VK22I%2BFY%2FIjMh2OQidlJmsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=9746d277\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/BlsobBB38IoVIDrct5mFQA</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/15s6xyl7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F15s6xyl7&h=dbc0e2ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1wbj3p59\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1wbj3p59&h=4c622f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/236805qz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F236805qz&h=30c3824b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9prqwfei\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9prqwfei&h=0fb9cafc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c838ce292d28e21fa5d6519b12c677929edfab59","tid":708521,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9225a69dce02f54ceb10246faa5fc0e5b24b53","tid":708521,"uid":160375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:21:17.000Z","msg":"玩咗8個鐘 又冇frd玩 就del咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f8531832f6568ff52c1fd6e1ae9f84a1919d5f","tid":708521,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d9225a69dce02f54ceb10246faa5fc0e5b24b53","tid":708521,"uid":160375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:21:17.000Z","msg":"玩咗8個鐘 又冇frd玩 就del咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:36:00.000Z","msg":"入黎1364一齊啦，我地經常有人係線上"},{"pid":"408f966597453e9b0016a5ef523b051c3c4315b3","tid":708521,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201